Description: Graphical proxy toggle for Linux
 Proxy GUI is a system tray application that allows you to
 easily toggle your proxy settings on and off. It supports
 Basic authentication forwarding via a local Python proxy.
 .
 Features:
  - System tray icon with on/off status
  - One-click toggle
  - Configuration window
  - Desktop notifications
  - Auto-start support
